            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green-400)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 3h4v4H3zM10 3h4v4h-4zM17 3h4v4h-4zM3 10h4v4H3zM10 10h4v4h-4zM17 10h4v4h-4zM3 17h4v4H3zM10 17h4v4h-4zM17 17h4v4h-4z"/></svg>
            <span>Nutrition</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wc-orbit-right">
        <span class="badge">Coordinated by Design</span>
        <h2 style="margin-top:1rem;">Your physician remains at <em>the center.</em></h2>
        <div class="wc-integration-list">
          <div class="wc-integration-item">
            <span class="wc-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p><strong>Direct communication.</strong> When we refer you to a Collective provider, we communicate directly — clinician to clinician — ensuring your care goals and clinical history are understood from day one.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="wc-integration-item">
            <span class="wc-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p><strong>Closed-loop follow-up.</strong> After your appointment, we follow up with your Collective provider and review progress at your next visit. Your care is not handed off — it's coordinated.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="wc-integration-item">
            <span class="wc-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p><strong>An evolving network.</strong> As the Collective grows and your needs change, your physician continuously refines referral recommendations. Member feedback directly shapes who we recruit next.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── 8. FAQ ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <FAQSection
